@startuml
title QA Gate Sanity Panel Plan

participant REV as "Reviewer"
participant QA as "QA Gate Panel"
participant QC as "QA Contract"
participant ACT as "QA Action Surface"
participant TL as "Tech Lead"

REV -> QA: APPROVE_IMPLEMENTATION
QA -> QA: workflow = qa_pending
QA -> QC: load sanity profile / runbook / expected evidence
QC --> QA: contract summary

QA -> ACT: Start QA
ACT -> ACT: collect sanityCommand / executionLog / fixtureUsed / outputVerified

alt validation fails
  ACT -> TL: REQUEST_CHANGES + failureEvidence
else validation passes
  ACT -> TL: APPROVE_IMPLEMENTATION + execution evidence
end

QA -> QA: render evidence card + gate outcome

@enduml
